einfo "network."
einfo
einfo "To use other Congestion Control other than Cubic, you must train a new"
einfo "learned model."
einfo
ewarn
ewarn "real-network.sh is in TESTING."
ewarn
ewarn
ewarn "FIXME:  The package indescriminately kills all running python instances."
ewarn
}

